lead_paragraph: When Nadia Comaneci takes her seat at the Rio Olympic Arena on Sunday, she will be able to sit back and follow the women's gymnastics competition untroubled by the pent-up tension she usually feels.

headline.print_headline: Gymnastics : Comaneci Laments Romania's Rio No-Show
